# Santander Dev Week - Backend

Backend for an web application built using Spring Boot at [Santander Dev Week](https://digitalinnovation.one/santander-dev-week-fullstack-developer)

After running, check the documentation at [`localhost:8080/bootcamp/swagger-ui.html`](http://localhost:8080/bootcamp/swagger-ui.html)
